NAME

    Mojolicious::Plugin::CORS

VERSION

    version 0.02

SYNOPSIS

        package App;
        use Mojo::Base 'Mojolicious';
    
        sub startup {
            my $self = shift;
    
            $self->plugin( 'Mojolicious::Plugin::CORS' );
        }

SUPPORT

 Bugs / Feature Requests

    Please report any bugs or feature requests through the issue tracker at
    https://github.com/sharabash/mojolicious-plugin-cors/issues. You will
    be notified automatically of any progress on your issue.

